


README
======

units4school
A Simple Tool to Generate Unit Tests for Physics Teachers 

Version: 	v0.05
Datum:		12.1.2019
Autor: 		F. Borchers


Questions from three different universes:
 + physical units
 + unit prefixes and
 + physical constants



PREREQUISITES
-------------

R, OpenOffice, pdflatex

Check on terminal with:
	R --version
	pdflatex --version
and
	soffice --version


RUN
---

Download the files into a directory and then run `make pdf`.







